# Runtime CMDB outputs (generated by sensory tools)
*-cmdb.json
!.claude/*-cmdb.json
!domains/laas/sensory-data/*-cmdb.json
# S6-DB-5 reference-deployment fixtures — these are committed example
# CMDBs that ship the docker-compose demo. Not runtime output.
!neurogrim-local-project/.claude/*-cmdb.json
!neurogrim-external-project/.claude/*-cmdb.json

# Brain runtime artifacts
.claude/brain/incident-ledger.json
.claude/brain/event-log.jsonl
.claude/brain/score-history.json
.claude/brain/proposal-ledger.json
.claude/brain/subagent-outcomes.jsonl
.claude/brain/subagent-health-cmdb.json
# Axis 4 v1 (2026-04-22) — Skill invocation ledger fed by the
# PostToolUse hook at scripts/record-skill-invocation.sh. Per-deployment
# runtime state; append-only JSONL.
.claude/brain/invocation-ledger.jsonl
# v5 V5-FOUND-1 (2026-05-02) — Diagnostics ledger emitted by the
# tracing Layer for timed operations (build/test/cargo/scoring/
# mcp_dispatch/a2a_post/a2a_sse/dashboard_route). Schema at
# neurogrim/crates/neurogrim-core/data/schemas/diagnostics-ledger-v1.schema.json.
# Per-deployment runtime state; never commit. Privacy floor enforced
# at write time (no prompts/args/payloads/free-text).
.claude/brain/diagnostics.jsonl
# v4.4 (2026-04-30) — bus topic SQLite stores: score-snapshots,
# services, skill-invocations, plus the v4.5 metrics TSDB. All
# per-deployment runtime state; created on first scoring run +
# rebuilt from canonical sources where applicable.
.claude/brain/queues/
.claude/brain/services.jsonl
# v4.0 S12-G-2 — `neurogrim test` quiet wrapper persists per-failure
# entries and rotates older entries to the archive. Both are
# per-deployment runtime state; failure history is local-only.
.claude/brain/test-failures.jsonl
.claude/brain/test-failures.archive.jsonl
# v4.0 S12-G-4 — `neurogrim publish-gate run` per-gate ledger;
# per-deployment governance trail of which gates passed/failed/are
# pending operator acknowledgement.
.claude/brain/publish-gate-ledger.jsonl
# v4.0 S12-G-5 — Playwright E2E artifacts (HTML report + per-test
# traces/screenshots). Regenerated on every `npm run e2e` invocation.
neurogrim/crates/neurogrim-dashboard/frontend/playwright-report/
neurogrim/crates/neurogrim-dashboard/frontend/test-results/
# E-SC-6 (2026-04-26) — supply-chain Layer 3 review framework runtime state.
# Decision ledger is operator-local audit trail; tickets are open-work files.
# Both per-deployment runtime state, not committed.
.claude/brain/supply-chain-tickets/
.claude/supply-chain-decision-ledger.jsonl
# E-SC-5 (2026-04-25) — supply-chain Layer 2 vigilance cache + per-package state.
.claude/brain/cache/vigilance/
# E-SC-8 (2026-04-26) — supply-chain calibration report (operator-local).
.claude/supply-chain-calibration-report.json
.claude/coherence-cmdb.json
# Agent-behavior verification state (spec §15 / S7-ABV). Feedback
# ledger is per-deployment; per-run result records are ephemeral.
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-feedback.jsonl
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-latest.json
.claude/brain/agent-behavior-runs/
# Judge-integrity ledger (S9-ABV-RED-3) — red-miss entries +
# triage decisions; per-deployment, never commit.
.claude/brain/judge-integrity-ledger.jsonl
# Domain-promotion ledger (S10-DP-2) — promotion / rollback /
# failed-attempt entries; per-deployment governance trail.
.claude/brain/domain-promotion-ledger.jsonl
# Audit artifacts (S10-DP-4) — calibrate + red-mode JSON reports
# per audit cycle; per-deployment, never commit.
.claude/brain/audit/

# Local machine awareness — machine-specific facts, never commit
.claude/brain/local-awareness.json

# Supply-chain SCA caches (E-SC-2): per-key OSV advisory responses
# cached for 24h. Regenerated on demand; never commit — the cache
# can balloon to thousands of entries in large workspaces and is
# fully reproducible from `neurogrim sensory supply-chain-sca`.
# The `**/` prefix matches .claude/brain/cache/ at any depth;
# NeuroGrim's unusual layout (repo-root .claude/ + neurogrim/
# workspace subdir) can produce caches in either location depending
# on which --project-root the operator scans.
**/.claude/brain/cache/

# Editor and OS
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# PowerShell
*.psm1.bak

# Node (whitepaper)
node_modules/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
dist/
# v3.4 — neurogrim-dashboard's frontend bundle MUST ship with the
# published crate (rust-embed reads it at compile time; users
# `cargo install` should not require Node.js). Negation overrides
# the generic `dist/` ignore above.
!neurogrim/crates/neurogrim-dashboard/frontend/dist/
!neurogrim/crates/neurogrim-dashboard/frontend/dist/**
.venv/
venv/

# Rust build artifacts
neurogrim/target/

# Test results
TestResults/
*.trx

# Verification script scratch dir (scripts/verify-external-brain.sh)
.verify-tmp/

# Claude Code session state (harness-managed, not source)
.claude/settings.local.json

# Cargo publish dry-run logs (ephemeral, machine-local)
neurogrim/.dry-run-logs/

# A2A bearer-token stores — machine-local, issued per deployment.
# Never commit.
**/a2a-tokens.sqlite
**/a2a-tokens.sqlite-shm
**/a2a-tokens.sqlite-wal
